</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>RW wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote"> As for my politics, I am an independent progressive after being a conservative dem for a number of years in Texas.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
